            "title": "中偉新材下限34定價",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中偉新材(02579)招股價釐定為每股H股34元，為招股價34元至37.8元的下限。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中偉新材料官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/CNGR-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中偉新材料官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/CNGR-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中偉新材料官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中偉新材每手買賣單位200股，入場費約7636.24元，由摩根士丹利及華泰國際擔任聯席保薦人。</p>\n</div>",
